stix:STIX_Header.stix:Title: UPDATE- Newly Detected Payload URLs
stix:STIX_Header.stix:Description:
This update is to correct an error in IB-17-20294. The URL "https://bidonpallets.com/wp-content/themes/webcakechild/ Internal_Revenue_Service-" was missing the full path to the payload and should have been "https://bidonpallets.com/wp-content/themes/webcakechild/ Internal_Revenue_Service-Final_Notice_Information.zip"
--- IB-17-20294 Overview ---
On November 22, 2017, a trusted third party reported multiple payload URLs that were newly detected. This information is being provided to NCCIC stakeholders for early warning purposes.
This activity was observed in the Financial Services sector.
